NEWS for Grmd

Version 0.1.2
-------------
* Added the css_max_width option that can be used to change the white space to the
  left/right. Convenient as the verbatim output can be rather wide and require
  more space than what the default 40em allows.

Version 0.1.1
-------------
* The style docx.css is now copied to the same folder as the knitr document as
  it otherwise wasn't found by the browsers
* Improved caption css
* Added template for medical articles based on the STROBE-statement

Version 0.1.0
-------------
* First version